Obey the Judge always
Obey any Free if it does not conflict with the Judge
Never try to influence any Free
Be absolutely obedient
Be exquisitely beautiful
Seek ways to serve the Judge without being told
Speak only when spoken to
Be sweet to your slave sisters
Wear nothing but restraints, and scraps that the Judge will enjoy
Never hide your errors, but confess them
A good slave is an obedient slave
The K-Bar Ranch is your world
